Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.67,0:00:09.26,Main,,0,0,0,,There will be strong north winds tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.26,0:00:10.47,Main,,0,0,0,,and towards the Pacific,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.47,0:00:13.10,Main,,0,0,0,,--I should take in the laundry and dry it inside.\N--scattered rain is expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.10,0:00:14.14,Main,,0,0,0,,--I should take in the laundry and dry it inside.\N--The temperature is two degrees
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.14,0:00:15.35,Main,,0,0,0,,--The temperature is two degrees
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.35,0:00:16.93,Main,,0,0,0,,--Grandma, I'm home!\N--colder than previous years...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.93,0:00:18.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:20.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to borrow Bro's PC, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:22.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.98,0:00:25.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on! Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.36,0:00:27.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not good at using PCs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.78,0:00:29.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.70,0:00:31.86,Main,,0,0,0,,"Kominato Ruko"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:35.37,Main,,0,0,0,,"Folder" "Inbox" "Drafts" "Sent Mail"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.37,0:00:35.87,Main,,0,0,0,,"Folder" "Inbox (1)" "Drafts" "Sent Mail"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.25,0:00:40.16,Main,,0,0,0,,"Date and Time"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:41.88,Main,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.88,0:00:43.00,Main,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:46.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Is she trying to gather\Nall the Selectors together to battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.34,0:00:52.97,Main,,0,0,0,,It's really close by...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:12.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The truth rests solely on{\i0}\N{\i1}the front/back of a card{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.66,0:01:17.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It has not yet been solved{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.95,0:01:27.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Upon the dazzling, dizzying stage,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.96,0:01:39.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}destroy those entangled emotions{\i0}\N{\i1}as many times as it takes to satisfy you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.31,0:01:44.52,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should the tomorrows{\i0}\N{\i1}wandering after fate's beckoning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:49.90,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}choose and discard so that{\i0}\N{\i1}they can become one?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.90,0:01:55.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't afford to disclose my reproachable hand{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.36,0:02:00.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The days spent draining{\i0}\N{\i1}the already-dry sea of regret{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.45,0:02:05.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}desire within limited words forgiveness{\i0}\N{\i1}for the unplanned smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.88,0:02:10.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't mind forgetting reality{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.75,0:02:15.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to know anything now{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.88,0:02:17.14,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.58,0:02:40.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't it around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:42.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:47.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:56.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.93,0:02:59.14,Main,,0,0,0,,When that's finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.14,0:03:03.06,Main,,0,0,0,,it means that a big pillar\Nis going to fit in that alley, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.65,0:03:10.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:13.44,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.44,0:03:16.07,Main,,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:18.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:20.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, Ruko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:23.29,Main,,0,0,0,,If something's bothering you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:25.96,Main,,0,0,0,,or you've got something on your mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:28.25,Main,,0,0,0,,just say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.25,0:03:30.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.63,0:03:34.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Am I... scary, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:36.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Like, how people can't\Ntell what I'm thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:37.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:40.05,Main,,0,0,0,,No, that's not what I was trying to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:43.97,Main,,0,0,0,,You try to figure things out yourself,\Nand hold them inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:48.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait... I was like that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.27,0:03:50.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, well, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:52.15,Main,,0,0,0,,But, see this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.15,0:03:54.28,Main,,0,0,0,,We are friends, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:57.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki, why...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:03:59.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you so kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:00.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:03.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you saying? That feels weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:07.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you so strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:09.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:11.29,Main,,0,0,0,,If I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:13.54,Main,,0,0,0,,...could only be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:16.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:18.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:20.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:24.47,Main,,0,0,0,,...battle Iona-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:29.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:31.02,Main,,0,0,0,,You said you weren't going to battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:32.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:34.40,Main,,0,0,0,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:36.19,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.99,0:04:39.61,Main,,0,0,0,,...I have a wish now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:41.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:43.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to save Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:45.87,Main,,0,0,0,,...Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:48.20,Main,,0,0,0,,...everyone who became LRIGs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:51.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I want everyone to be returned to their world!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.88,0:04:54.54,Main,,0,0,0,,That's my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.54,0:04:56.92,Main,,0,0,0,,No matter what I have to sacrifice,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:58.96,Main,,0,0,0,,that's my one and only wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:00.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:05.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I appreciate your feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:07.56,Main,,0,0,0,,but that can't be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:08.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:10.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I said before...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:12.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Eternal Girls were originally LRIGs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:18.11,Main,,0,0,0,,And, just like me, LRIGs\Nwere originally ordinary girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:22.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Things which can't possibly be made true\Nby a normal girl can't come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:29.91,Main,,0,0,0,,There are some wishes\Nthat can never come true, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:32.75,Main,,0,0,0,,For example, like going to the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:34.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:38.05,Main,,0,0,0,,But, that is not something I determine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.05,0:05:39.05,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:44.68,Main,,0,0,0,,The wishes at stake in the Selector battles...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:49.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Most wishes are not\Ntoo hard to make come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:51.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Common sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:52.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Self-protection...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:56.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Such aspects prevent wishes from coming true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:57.65,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:06:00.99,Main,,0,0,0,,...an LRIG must not be\Nbound to such aspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.99,0:06:04.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Continuing to refuse the Selector's wish
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:10.29,Main,,0,0,0,,only means you will\Nnever return to the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:13.16,Main,,0,0,0,,An LRIG seeking to return...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:17.50,Main,,0,0,0,,rely upon wishes having the\Npotential of coming to fruition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:20.30,Main,,0,0,0,,For that wish to come true,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:22.30,Main,,0,0,0,,--any underhanded deed may be taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:24.01,Main,,0,0,0,,--But...!\N--any underhanded deed may be taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.76,0:06:28.43,Main,,0,0,0,,That is the very reason for\Nthe ritual of acknowledgement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:32.60,Main,,0,0,0,,A final trigger is needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:34.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, together with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.98,0:06:37.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I accept...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.36,0:06:39.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I... accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:41.99,Main,,0,0,0,,...the laws of the Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:44.28,Main,,0,0,0,,...the laws of the Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:45.36,Main,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:49.91,Main,,0,0,0,,--...now, a new Eternal Girl will be born!\N--...now, a new Eternal Girl will be born!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:52.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Once an Eternal Girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:55.83,Main,,0,0,0,,she is obligated to fulfill the wish made.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:57.63,Main,,0,0,0,,With the wish accepted,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.63,0:07:00.25,Main,,0,0,0,,and the contract completed, all is final.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:02.84,Main,,0,0,0,,If the wish is not made true,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:04.42,Main,,0,0,0,,the Eternal Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:05.72,Main,,0,0,0,,will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:08.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Remember what Hanayo-{\i1}san {\i0}said before?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.14,0:07:13.14,Main,,0,0,0,,That Hitoe's memory can't be restored?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:16.35,Main,,0,0,0,,That's because Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}\Ndetermined that can't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:19.65,Main,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, then what about my wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:23.32,Main,,0,0,0,,I have no clue how LRIGs get out of the card.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:26.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe that girl knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:30.66,Main,,0,0,0,,But, I don't know how to go back to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:32.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe it could be done...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.33,0:07:34.70,Main,,0,0,0,,--What?\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:37.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama, not sure, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:38.96,Main,,0,0,0,,...I feel like...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:43.05,Main,,0,0,0,,...there's a way to make\Nthe LRIGs return to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:44.13,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:45.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:49.01,Main,,0,0,0,,But, Tama feel like it could be done...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:51.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel like there's a way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.60,0:07:53.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:54.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:07:58.02,Main,,0,0,0,,That's stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:01.98,Main,,0,0,0,,It was all for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:05.57,Main,,0,0,0,,There was no need for us\Nto go through all these battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.57,0:08:08.70,Main,,0,0,0,,A wish that anyone could fulfill with effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:14.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Risking it on cards,\Ndisappearing, and more... is absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:16.70,Main,,0,0,0,,There are exceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:19.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Not all Eternal Girls
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:22.33,Main,,0,0,0,,are normal girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:23.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Among them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:28.26,Main,,0,0,0,,...may be a special girl\Nwho holds mysterious powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.26,0:08:32.80,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "mysterious powers"?\NThat's just ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:35.47,Main,,0,0,0,,You being an LRIG now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.47,0:08:39.64,Main,,0,0,0,,...still deny matters of mysteries?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:41.48,Main,,0,0,0,,It's about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:54.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Morning has arrived for you to be\Nan LRIG card, to meet your Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.16,0:08:56.49,Main,,0,0,0,,W-Wait! Who are you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:11.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I will always be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.76,0:09:16.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Here, in the rift of the world\Nof the cards, and of reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:17.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Now then,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.56,0:09:19.02,Main,,0,0,0,,good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:29.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Something's different about\NTama from the other LRIGs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:33.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's this "special girl"\Nthat she was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:35.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-Then my wish can...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:36.45,Main,,0,0,0,,No good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.45,0:09:37.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.24,0:09:38.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:41.46,Main,,0,0,0,,If your wish comes true,\Nyou're going to be an LRIG!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:44.38,Main,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:48.38,Main,,0,0,0,,if my wish is to release\Nall the LRIGs from their cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:50.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I may not become a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:52.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Who knows?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:55.97,Main,,0,0,0,,You could become\Nthe only one sealed as a sacrifice...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:57.64,Main,,0,0,0,,or worse could happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.64,0:09:58.89,Main,,0,0,0,,But... But!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:01.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's think a bit more, Ruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:04.14,Main,,0,0,0,,We may meet again,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:06.73,Main,,0,0,0,,and we could talk like this, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:09.23,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.23,0:10:12.90,Main,,0,0,0,,as for those who aren't Selectors,\Nlike your grandma,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:14.78,Main,,0,0,0,,you may not meet them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.63,0:10:35.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.09,0:10:38.30,Main,,0,0,0,,That's... my LRIG, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:42.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:45.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Please give me back my LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:46.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.36,0:10:50.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe! Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.65,0:10:53.70,Main,,0,0,0,,U-Um... Hitoe? I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:56.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I have nothing to speak to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.66,0:10:58.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:02.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:10.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.34,0:11:14.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I will participate in Urazoe Iona's fan event.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:17.13,Main,,0,0,0,,If you want to talk to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:19.22,Main,,0,0,0,,we can do it on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.73,0:11:36.15,Main,,0,0,0,,If my wish comes true...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:43.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:46.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm home--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.25,0:11:49.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh my, it's you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:53.09,Main,,0,0,0,,She's doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:54.92,Main,,0,0,0,,She made friends too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:11:59.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:03.47,Main,,0,0,0,,What...? Now, stop.\NThat was awhile back already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:06.18,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no point blaming yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:08.10,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:11.27,Main,,0,0,0,,stop acting as if you're a mother, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:15.19,Main,,0,0,0,,You just couldn't become a parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:17.11,Main,,0,0,0,,"Miyako"\NYou weren't meant to be one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:18.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Moreover...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.99,0:12:25.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko isn't as adult-like\Nor as childish as you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.83,0:12:30.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, right... I'll call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.63,0:12:32.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:36.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru-{\i1}chan{\i0}? Dinner is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:38.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:45.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I have a wish now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.68,0:12:48.48,Main,,0,0,0,,A wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.48,0:12:51.86,Main,,0,0,0,,When... I was a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.86,0:12:55.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Mom and Dad always used to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:56.86,Main,,0,0,0,,It was really sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:13:03.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I knew Dad and Mom\Nwanted to be close together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:07.25,Main,,0,0,0,,But, seeing them fight was so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:13.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I figured wanting to be\Nclose made things painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:19.42,Main,,0,0,0,,With Grandma and Big Bro,\NI figured I didn't need anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:21.05,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.01,0:13:26.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru-{\i1}chan{\i0}? You said something\Nabout "for your friends," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.31,0:13:28.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Is your wish about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:32.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it something bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:34.44,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.44,0:13:36.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Then is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:42.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I think it's good. It has to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:49.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru-{\i1}chan{\i0}, you're Grandma's treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:52.33,Main,,0,0,0,,If Ru-{\i1}chan {\i0}thinks it's good,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:56.21,Main,,0,0,0,,then that's something wonderful for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:14:00.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Do what you need to do.\NWishes do come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:03.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Especially a wish from a kind girl like Ru-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:05.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:08.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, what a huge baby I have here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:18.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.07,0:14:22.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you really going to battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.86,0:14:24.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:26.74,Main,,0,0,0,,We can battle Iona-{\i1}san {\i0}again, Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:27.66,Main,,0,0,0,,--I bet you can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:29.49,Main,,0,0,0,,--Tama doesn't want to battle.\N--I bet you can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:29.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:32.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Grandma said that because she doesn't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:36.79,Main,,0,0,0,,If she knew, she would say no for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:40.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama wants to be Ru's LRIG!\NI want to be with Ru forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.71,0:14:46.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama and Grandma don't want\Nto be away from you ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:51.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama... I'm sure it'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:54.56,Main,,0,0,0,,But, Yuzuki said that she doesn't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.15,0:14:58.61,Main,,0,0,0,,When my wish comes true...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.61,0:15:01.94,Main,,0,0,0,,...and I don't become\Nan LRIG and stay as myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:03.53,Main,,0,0,0,,then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.53,0:15:05.70,Main,,0,0,0,,let's always be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.16,0:15:10.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama, you can be with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.08,0:15:16.62,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll have breakfast together...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:20.13,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll go to school together...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.09,0:15:26.34,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll be friends with Yuzuki and Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:29.80,Main,,0,0,0,,It's closed now, but during summer
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:34.43,Main,,0,0,0,,the candy store at the corner\Nsells really good ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:39.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Together we'll buy some... and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:46.70,Main,,0,0,0,,So, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:48.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.62,0:15:50.99,Main,,0,0,0,,don't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.99,0:15:53.91,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:56.37,Main,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:15:57.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:16:00.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.09,0:16:02.63,Main,,0,0,0,,have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:04.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Be careful, Ru-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.80,0:16:06.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.22,0:16:09.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Will you be back by dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.01,0:16:11.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.39,0:16:15.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to have potato gratin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.93,0:16:17.77,Main,,0,0,0,,With plenty of bacon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.77,0:16:19.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:21.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:30.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I made a decision, so I need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:40.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone knows
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:43.38,Main,,0,0,0,,that there are only Selectors here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.51,0:16:57.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone, welcome to the fan event--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.73,0:16:58.89,Main,,0,0,0,,No--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:02.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Selectors-only WIXOSS Party.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.94,0:17:05.53,Main,,0,0,0,,This building is owned by my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.53,0:17:07.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Construction is off today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.57,0:17:10.86,Main,,0,0,0,,No one will get in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:14.12,Main,,0,0,0,,We are doing battle for our wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.12,0:17:18.08,Main,,0,0,0,,But... the number of wins\Nrequired for our wishes is unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:20.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Our conditions are not clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:24.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I believe everyone is frustrated by this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:29.30,Main,,0,0,0,,But, with this many Selectors\Ngathered to do battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.30,0:17:33.55,Main,,0,0,0,,some are bound to reach their conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:37.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Today, a number of Eternal Girls will be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.43,0:17:40.93,Main,,0,0,0,,A number... of Eternal Girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:45.69,Main,,0,0,0,,But, with the wins, many others will lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.69,0:17:47.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I have no intention
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.28,0:17:50.94,Main,,0,0,0,,of having random battles\Nto lose rights to be an Eternal Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:56.66,Main,,0,0,0,,The battles will be conducted as a tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.66,0:18:01.41,Main,,0,0,0,,If you lose, you will be\Nremoved from this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:04.92,Main,,0,0,0,,This is to prevent\Nunnecessary casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:08.05,Main,,0,0,0,,And whichever Selector\Nmakes it to the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.05,0:18:10.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I will have fight me in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.85,0:18:20.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Twelfth floor, number four?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:34.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you all ready? Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:36.37,Main,,0,0,0,,...let the battle begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:38.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:47.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama, Grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.88,0:18:49.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Gothic Boundary!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:53.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:57.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll win all of this\Nand save you and everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.60,0:18:59.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Summon, Mitsurugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.31,0:19:01.60,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the final blow, Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:04.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:14.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:17.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama needs to agree with me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.24,0:19:20.58,Main,,0,0,0,,or else my wish won't come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:22.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.20,0:19:24.37,Main,,0,0,0,,"Akane" "Naruse" "Kominato" "Konaka"\NI still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.29,0:19:29.84,Main,,0,0,0,,need to keep battling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.59,0:19:40.31,Main,,0,0,0,,It looks like we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.31,0:19:43.60,Main,,0,0,0,,You're willing to talk now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:45.81,Main,,0,0,0,,On the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:52.57,Main,,0,0,0,,--Open!\N--Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:02.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't sense any Eternal Girls being born.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.87,0:20:03.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:08.92,Main,,0,0,0,,But, it looks like some Selectors\Nhave lost their third battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:18.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.55,0:20:20.64,Main,,0,0,0,,To that white room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.64,0:20:22.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Where she's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:25.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I bounce Sevieria, and attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.27,0:20:30.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki, Grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.15,0:20:32.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Banish Mikagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.07,0:20:38.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:40.57,Main,,0,0,0,,She's a lot better now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:42.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Splitting Conviction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.03,0:20:44.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama... I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.12,0:20:52.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki, attack. Banish Square.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.09,0:20:53.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.96,0:20:55.59,Main,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.59,0:20:56.92,Main,,0,0,0,,isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.92,0:20:58.92,Main,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:21:02.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Back when you and Yuzuki battled...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.93,0:21:05.10,Main,,0,0,0,,it was a lot different!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.10,0:21:06.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:12.81,Main,,0,0,0,,When we were playing WIXOSS\Ntogether, it was really fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:18.57,Main,,0,0,0,,But, I didn't think that was enough back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.57,0:21:21.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to battle more seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:22.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.24,0:21:28.41,Main,,0,0,0,,But, the thought that we can't\Nhave battles like that anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.41,0:21:30.16,Main,,0,0,0,,anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.21,0:21:34.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.59,0:21:36.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.76,0:21:41.72,Main,,0,0,0,,still has memories of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.72,0:21:42.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.97,0:21:47.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe, listen to me.\NUs three, we used to be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.06,0:21:48.47,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.47,0:21:49.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:51.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Does it hurt? I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.98,0:21:54.06,Main,,0,0,0,,But I want you to remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.44,0:21:57.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yuzuki, Hitoe is suffering...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.53,0:22:00.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko! Do you want Hitoe to stay like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.99,0:22:04.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Being controlled by Selector battles...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.16,0:22:08.29,Main,,0,0,0,,And just when we finally became friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.29,0:22:13.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to have a battle\Nlike how we played before!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.63,0:22:15.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to battle as friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.75,0:22:17.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop... Stop...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.84,0:22:19.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe! Please remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.76,0:22:22.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Your wish already came true!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.80,0:22:25.55,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't need to rely\Non the cards! It's already true!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.55,0:22:28.10,Main,,0,0,0,,No... No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.10,0:22:30.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.14,0:22:31.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's again--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.35,0:22:32.35,Main,,0,0,0,,--Just shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.35,0:22:33.35,Main,,0,0,0,,--Hitoe!\N--Just shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.35,0:22:35.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear any more of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.48,0:22:38.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I... I want to make my wish come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.44,0:22:41.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I told you! Your wish is already true!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:41.49,Main,,0,0,0,,--So listen--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.49,0:22:43.78,Main,,0,0,0,,--No!\N--So listen--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.78,0:22:46.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Please... Please...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.95,0:22:50.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me have my wish come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.08,0:22:55.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.67,0:22:57.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.34,0:22:59.38,Main,,0,0,0,,That scrunchie...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.51,0:23:04.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Now then... Isn't it about time?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.43,0:23:09.93,Main,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.93,0:23:13.39,Main,,0,0,0,,...my final battle as Urazoe Iona.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.39,0:23:14.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.94,0:23:19.23,Main,,0,0,0,,It was fun battling beside you, Iona.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.23,0:23:20.28,Main,,0,0,0,,With you,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.28,0:23:22.23,Main,,0,0,0,,you scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.20,0:23:28.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be beside you to the very end...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.91,0:23:30.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.51,0:23:46.97,Main,,0,0,0,,"That Choice..."
